Uses of Interface
commands.Command

  • Packages that use Command 
    Package Description
    commands  
    recordables  

    • Uses of Command in commands

      Classes in commands that implement Command 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  Copy
      The copy command, asks the engine to execute the copy
      class  Cut
      The cut command, asks the engine to execute the cut.
      class  DeleteText
      The delete text command, asks the engine to execute the text deletion.
      class  InsertText
      The insert text command, asks the engine to execute the text insertion.
      class  Paste
      The paste command, asks the engine to execute the paste.
      class  Redo
      Redo is to ask the engine to undo the last undo done (if possible).
      class  Replay
      Replay asks the recorder to replay the previously recorded commands.
      class  Select
      The selection command, asks the engine to execute a selection.
      class  Start
      Start asks the recorder to start recording commands for future replay.
      class  Stop
      Stop asks the recorder to stop recording commands.
      class  Undo
      Undo is to ask the engine to undo the last command (if possible).

    • Uses of Command in recordables

      Subinterfaces of Command in recordables 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      interface  CommandRecordable
      CommandRecordable is implemented by the recordable commands.
      Classes in recordables that implement Command 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  CopyRecordable
      CopyRecordable executes a copy command will saving its state in a recorder.
      class  CutRecordable
      CutRecordable executes a cut command will saving its state in a recorder.
      class  DelTextRecordable
      DelTextRecordable executes a text deletion command will saving its state in a recorder.
      class  InsTextRecordable
      InsTextRecordable executes a text insertion command will saving its state in a recorder.
      class  PasteRecordable
      PasteRecordable executes a text insertion command will saving its state in a recorder.
      class  SelectRecordable
      SelectRecordable executes a select command will saving its state in a recorder.
